  <section class='page-section confectionary intro'>
  <div class='container'>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <h1>About Easy-Fit</h1>

        <p>Working from two new purpose built factories, and with many years experience in manufacturing we have the right balance between staff who are totally conscientious in their approach, and state of the art manufacturing machinery and technology. With investments in machinery up to now this year alone of over £200,000, we are investing in the our business to ensure that we maintain the highest levels of quality and service. This is combined with our ongoing and continuous efforts, to improve the product we supply, and the way we supply it to make it easier to install, and thus easier for the installer.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <img src="/images/apex.png" alt="" />
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-12">
        <p>We understand the need to supply customers orders complete and on time, and as a trade only fabricator, our customers can be sure that we are concentrating on their needs, and not diluting our efforts with domestic installations.</p>

        <h2 style='font-weight: normal;'>The <b>Easy-Fit</b> Brand</h2>

        <p>We developed the ‘easy-fit’ brand to be synonymous with our company ethos, and the needs of installers. We manufacture a complete range of products, in both PVCu and Aluminium to provide a ‘One Stop Shop’ for our customers saving both time and money in deliveries, ordering etc., and having one point of call for all information, technical or otherwise.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>



